thread.title: AND International Publishers enters into agreement to license mapping data to U.S. company
thread.title_full: BRIEF-AND International Publishers enters into agreement to license mapping data to U.S. company | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: AND International Publishers enters into agreement to license mapping data to U.S. company
text:
Sept 25 And International Publishers NV :
* Announces that it has entered into a material agreement to license certain mapping data to a U.S.-based company.
* Expects strong revenue growth for 2015 compared to 2014
* Expects to realise a profit in 2015 comparable to realised profit in 2014 Source text for Eikon: (Gdynia Newsroom)
